Alberiz's Grocer on Dell Avenue got cards on the wall.

1359
02:17:21,151 --> 02:17:22,192
好，谢谢
Yeah, thanks.

1360
02:17:33,413 --> 02:17:36,081
不是他，不是克里斯
It's not him. It's not Chris.

1361
02:17:43,757 --> 02:17:45,883
第二小组，这是指挥部
Unit 2, this is Command.

1362
02:17:46,051 --> 02:17:48,719
拦阻他并查看身份
Take him at the street and check him out.

1363
02:17:48,887 --> 02:17:50,387
收到
