- 我们仍有诱饵，也许还有时间！ - 有，我们有什么？
- We still got bait. Maybe some time! - Got, got. What do we got?

1383
02:20:13,531 --> 02:20:15,365
我们有什么？
What do we got?

1384
02:20:15,784 --> 02:20:18,452
旅途愉快，杂种
Bon voyage, motherfucker.

1385
02:20:19,162 --> 02:20:21,371
你很行
You were good.

1386
02:20:22,457 --> 02:20:23,999
我要去住旅馆
I'm going to the hotel.

1387
02:20:25,418 --> 02:20:27,878
我要去洗澡
I'm gonna take a shower.

1388
02:20:28,463 --> 02:20:31,965
睡一个月的觉
Gonna sleep for a month.

1389
02:22:41,888 --> 02:22:43,680
用这个
Over here.

1390
