浑蛋经常自毁，你不会死的 宝贝，你不会的
Assholes shoot themselves all fucking day. Not you, baby. Not you.

1397
02:23:26,224 --> 02:23:29,685
她会在哪里？她叫萝伦 萝伦古丝塔芙森
Where would she be? Her name is Lauren, Lauren Gustafson.

1398
02:23:29,852 --> 02:23:32,104
她应该在这里，但警方告诉我···
I'm supposed to be here with her. But the police...

1399
02:23:39,028 --> 02:23:42,197
- 我需要人帮忙··· - 没关系，我可以
- Help me. I need somebody to help... - It's okay.

1400
02:23:43,658 --> 02:23:45,242
我抱着你
I got you.

1401
02:23:47,870 --> 02:23:49,037
我抱着你，宝贝
I got you, baby.

1402
02:23:50,373 --> 02:23:53,709
你会没事的，亲爱的 会没事的，我保证
It'll be all right, honey. I swear. It's okay, baby.

1403
02:23:53,876 --> 02:23:57,921
找医生来！我要医生！你妈妈在这
Let's get a doctor! Let's go! A doctor here! There's your mama.

1404
02:23:58,089 --> 02:23:59,965
- 冷静下来 - 你妈妈在这
- Let's just calm down. - Your mama's here.

1405
02:24:00,133 --> 02:24:01,967
- 她有服用药物吗？ - 没有
- Is she on any drugs? - No.

1406
02:24:04,887 --> 02:24:07,681
找创伤及血管外科医生来
I want you to get a trauma surgeon and a vascular surgeon.

1407
02:24:07,849 --> 02:24:11,101
