Her pressure's down. So is her respiration. You have to intubate her.

1409
02:24:14,772 --> 02:24:16,481
准备好了
It's ready.

1410
02:24:17,984 --> 02:24:21,153
- 最后一次任何人见到她是何时？ - 我不知道
- When's the last time anybody saw her? - I don't know.

1411
02:24:21,321 --> 02:24:24,406
- 你在哪里找到她的？ - 浴缸
- Where did you find her? - The bathtub.

1412
02:24:24,574 --> 02:24:28,118
