Hi. Your daughter's out of surgery and she's in the recovery room now, okay?

1419
02:24:51,309 --> 02:24:55,479
她情况稳定 医生很快会出来跟你们解释
Her vital signs are stable. The surgeon will be out to speak to you in a few moments.

1420
02:24:55,646 --> 02:24:57,522
- 她没事吧？ - 她很好
- She's okay? - She's doing good.

1421
02:24:57,690 --> 02:24:59,858
- 她会没事的 - 她会没事的
- She's gonna be okay. - She's gonna be okay.

1422
02:25:00,026 --> 02:25:02,903
- 她不会有事 - 我的宝贝
- Oh, my baby. - She's gonna be okay. It's all right.

1423
02:25:03,071 --> 02:25:06,198
- 没事了 - 她为何这样对自己？
- It's all right. - Why'd she do this to herself? Why?

1424
02:25:06,366 --> 02:25:10,577
看她把自己怎么了
Look what she did. Look what she did to herself.

1425
02:25:11,621 --> 02:25:13,455
别难过
There.

1426
02:25:13,873 --> 02:25:16,792
没事的，不会有事的
It's all right, honey. It's gonna be all right.

1427
02:25:16,959 --> 02:25:19,002
我在这里，我哪里也不去
I'm here. I ain't going anywhere.

1428
02:25:19,170 --> 02:25:20,212
- 明白吗？ - 好
- You understand? - Yeah.

1429
02:25:20,380 --> 02:25:22,464
我哪里也不去
I ain't going anywhere.

1430
02:25:35,269 --> 02:25:36,269
是？
Yeah?

1431
02:25:36,771 --> 02:25:37,771
是我
It's me.

1432
02:25:38,356 --> 02:25:41,608
飞机己在半空，会准时抵达
Plane's in the air now. It'll be right on time.

1433
02:25:41,818 --> 02:25:45,821
仍找不到可信任的司机
On the driver's end, I still can't find nobody, so that's in the trust.

1434
02:25:45,988 --> 02:25:47,864
还有一事
One other thing.

1435
02:25:48,324 --> 02:25:49,908
你既然问了，我就告诉你
You asked, so I gotta tell you.

1436
02:25:50,743 --> 02:25:53,620
你要找的人在马奎斯酒店 化名“詹姆森”
The guy you wanted checked into the Marquis under "Jameson"...

1437
02:25:53,788 --> 02:25:57,165
如果你还在乎他的话 我猜你不会想找他
...if you still give a shit, which I figured you wouldn't.

1438
02:25:57,333 --> 02:26:01,086
- 你说得对 - 再见，兄弟
- You figured right. - So, so long, brother.

1439
02:26:02,797 --> 02:26:04,756
