1445
02:27:06,903 --> 02:27:08,570
有的
There's time.

1446
02:27:36,974 --> 02:27:40,101
我很快回来，车子不要熄火
I'll be right back. Just leave her running.

1447
02:28:21,519 --> 02:28:23,979
- 入住登记 - 是，这是客房服务
- Registration. - Yeah, this is Room Service.

1448
02:28:24,146 --> 02:28:27,983
