- I'll stay. - No, I'm okay. I can... I can handle this.

1473
02:32:16,378 --> 02:32:18,379
你自己小心
Just be careful.

1474
02:32:18,631 --> 02:32:21,382
打电话到这里给我，让我知道你没事
Call me here. Let me know you're okay.

1475
02:32:22,301 --> 02:32:23,843
好吗？
Okay?

1476
02:33:05,719 --> 02:33:06,761
走楼梯
Take the stairs.

1477
02:33:20,734 --> 02:33:21,776
谁？
Yeah?

1478
